column5: thought i could beat the rain ☔️
way too hot, was sweating before i’d left the car park

hard to not be disappointed with this one. after a huge day out i was agonisingly close to home but the knee just had nothing left and i had to call it. everything up to bacchus marsh was great, victoria is fricken beautiful.
bit more of a push but something’s still not quite right
lol i gotta go see a physio
